name: Smell of woods
description_long: Keep warm with the cozy Domino wool throw from Klippan Yllefabrik. Klippan Yllefabric was founded in 1879 with a philosophy to combine Swedish design with the traditional knowledge of textiles. This particular throw has a simple, classic pattern design and is available in different colors.

name: Evil believe
description_long: The beautiful Rustic mug from House Doctor is made of ceramics and has an appealing glaze in grey and blue that contributes to a rustic feeling. Since it's handmade, every mug is unique. Match it with other Hand Cream in the Rustic series.

name: BERGASANDAL
description_long: The herbaceous aroma of chamomile, rich and sweet as honey, forms a subtle harmony with bitter clary sage for an addictive aroma.Moist moss that feels cold, wrapped in elegant soft grained blond wood and warm musk, presents a special and small comfort to your weary soul.
